# Core Data Architecture

## Never Create Niche Tables

No `bourbons`, `movies`, `albums`, `books`, `teams` tables.

Use: `entity_types`, `entities`, `entity_attributes`, `entity_relationships`

## Collections Are Crown Jewel

```txt
User → Collection → Entities
```

## Reputation Before Launch

Tables exist now: `user_reputation`, `user_badges`, `user_expertise`, `user_contributions`

Authority, not gamification.

## Content Engine

`@foundry/content-engine` generates 11 content types per topic/entity automatically.

## Packages

- `@foundry/content-engine` — CMS + SEO factory
- `@foundry/seo-engine` — structured data + entity paths
- `@foundry/knowledge-graph` — aligns with entity_relationships

